{"tid":1809240,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"kfc係藍店，但為咗打擊麥當勞氣焰，我宣布呢八日暫時准許大家食kfc","createTime":"2020-01-03T02:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T04:59:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e825e8ec2985a450218279cbae040a885c6af323","tid":1809240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:54:18.000Z","msg":"香港咁多人，實有一啲垃圾軟弱無志氣嘅人，提少陣就會去食番金拱門或者冷門藍店，上咗幾個麥當勞post已經見到有幾個user到依家仲未知麥當勞衰乜想繼續食，所以絕對唔能夠睇小宣傳罷食，呢八日好明顯係造勢大會，就算蝕錢做都唔介意，總之呢八日一定要多人，大家唔可以畀麥當勞得呈！！！起碼要忍八日！！我已經無食兩個月，嚟緊都唔會再食！！"},{"pid":"57b0ce262550e740c0af1031a2850545fa61ee52","tid":1809240,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:59:10.000Z","msg":"KFC唔係因為響生果報落廣告比我哋偉大ge港獨之父點名嘉許咩？"},{"pid":"f6e0cfbdc95a39d3074ac23898679a22612c7ddc","tid":1809240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"香港人好善忘所以要𣎴斷提醒，好多人都係一唔提就會食番"},{"pid":"1efb5e9011cd4f51d0bb20f6711b9ea9e89531b4","tid":1809240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57b0ce262550e740c0af1031a2850545fa61ee52","tid":1809240,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:59:10.000Z","msg":"KFC唔係因為響生果報落廣告比我哋偉大ge港獨之父點名嘉許咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"shk"},{"pid":"8428128a6711d420e0a94b643287cb93ab09e1d5","tid":1809240,"uid":217383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:03:24.000Z","msg":"Sor 兩間都唔撚會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼錢都唔撚會食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aff080fdbfa19c5b4541120194b6f249b8d8652","tid":1809240,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"弱智仔"},{"pid":"6d92b486e4252ee6e82b2166aa4b9142c1bf873c","tid":1809240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a